text:
(1) North River, New York's skyline, looking north from the mouth of the River.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The North River, shown from the harbor; looking north from the mouth.

P. L. Sperr.

(3) The same as view 2, at an earlier date. The ferry boat is that of the Central Railroad of New Jersey.

P. L. Sperr.
